Have you tried having a tea break with your cat(s)?. 
We love our tea time together. When he hears me making tea, he comes and asks for some as well. If you do this, make sure the catnip tea has cooled down before giving it to your cat. The first part of the video is an oldie. He drinks his tea from a flat bowl to prevent whisker fatigue.
